title: Talks Machina Ep. 53 - Talking C2E4 'Disparate Pieces'
description:
Voice actor Matthew Mercer leads a group of fellow voice actors on epic Dungeons & Dragons campaigns. These familiar voices bring the audience into the full experience of D&D, allowing imaginations to soar as the characters embark on adventures. This is Critical Role! 

Watch live on Thursdays at 7PM PT on Twitch, Youtube, or the live enhanced version on Alpha. 

Included is the following episode ripped from projectalpha.com 


1. Talks Machina Ep. 52 - Talking Critical Role C2E4 'Disparate Pieces' 


Most episodes were re-encoded using the software Handbrake's Very Fast 720p30 preset depending on the source resolution which varied per episode
